EVERYDAY GOALS: An application that builds up a simple and ready to ToDo list to kick start your day and also reminds you about your tasks at the end of the day.

This application helps a person to create a regular To Do List. It supports adding and deleting items on the go, deleting multiple items as a batch, and a reminder for uncompleted items till the end of the day. The app is quite user friendly and will hence help in improving productivity of the user.


We welcome feedback on Everyday Goals,suggestions for new or improved features.
https://github.com/AayushChaturvedi

