2.PROBLEMS IT SOLVES

a-Management of the daily tasks needed to be done in this world of messed up schedule of individuals.
b-Easy handling of the app and user friendly.

3.DOWNLOADING INSTRUCTION

a-Download the apk from package.
b.Click on apk.
c.It will download automatically and ask for necessary permissions.

4.USER MANUAL

a.Click on launcher icon.
b.Add the tasks to be done.
c.Press "ADD A NEW TASK".
d.It also has a count of number of tasks to be done.
e.Once the task is done, Select the "DONE!" option and it will delete the task.
f.Subsequently the number of tasks needed to be done also reduces.
g.Prompts before quiting the app.

5.KNOWN ISSUES AT RELEASE

a.The list is not saved means the app is needed to run in the background.
b."ADD A NEW TASK" button itself doesn't shift the writing position to another tab, it needed to be done manually.





